oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Strickland sketch of Corinthian capital
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Plate 41 of a collection of seventy-three original drawings belonging to William Strickland. The sketch shows detail of a Corinthian capital and design for acanthus leaves.
